---
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-background">
    <img src="/images/hero-bg.png" alt="Transport professionnel Sam's Transport" />
    <div class="overlay"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container hero-content animate-fade">
    <div class="badge">Basé à Vauréal (95)</div>
    <h1>Déménagement, transport et débarras en <span class="accent-text">Île‑de‑France</span> et dans <span class="accent-text">toute la France</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">SAM’S TRANSPORT, basée au 87 boulevard de l’Oise à Vauréal, vous accompagne pour vos déménagements, débarras, transports d’objets lourds et prestations de nettoyage principalement en Île‑de‑France et dans toute la France.</p>
    <p class="hero-text">Un seul interlocuteur, une équipe sérieuse et réactive, des interventions rapides et organisées : nous simplifions vos projets, du premier contact jusqu’à la remise des clés.</p>
    
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/devis" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Demander un devis gratuit</a>
      <a href="tel:0123456789" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Nous appeler maintenant</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-value">100%</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Réactivité</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-value">National</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Île‑de‑France & France</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-value">Gratuit</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Devis & Conseils</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--white);
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-top: 120px;
    padding-bottom: 60px;
  }
  
  .hero-background {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: -1;
  }
  
  .hero-background img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  
  .overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(10, 37, 64, 0.9) 0%, rgba(10, 37, 64, 0.6) 50%, rgba(10, 37, 64, 0.2) 100%);
  }
  
  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    padding-top: 0;
  }
  
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    border: 1px solid var(--secondary);
    color: var(--secondary);
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  
  .accent-text {
    color: var(--secondary);
  }
  
  p {
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 700px;
  }
  
  .hero-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  
  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  .btn-lg {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  .btn-outline {
    border-color: var(--white);
    color: var(--white);
  }
  
  .btn-outline:hover {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .stat-value {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }
  
  .stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      height: auto;
      padding: 120px 0 60px;
    }
    
    .hero-content {
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .hero-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }
    
    .hero-stats {
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .stat-divider {
      display: none;
    }
    
    .overlay {
      background: rgba(10, 37, 64, 0.8);
    }
  }
</style>
